name: 〜(￣▽￣〜) R U M B I T A   W O R L D   I N V I T A T I O N (〜￣▽￣)〜
description:
Start getting ready! 🍄 ✨

Today SHROOMIES is opening its magical mushroom doors to a selected group of humanoids. Get ready to celebrate the grand opening and forget about your problems for a few hours. 

We separated a table for you in the VIP area. 

Open bar from 11:11pm til 3:33am, enjoy a delicious Fueguito shot 🔥 on the house ♌️
